applyOperator

public OMCRangeList applyOperator(ConstraintOperator op)
Return a value that is the equivalent under the IN ConstraintOperator to this value under the given operator. For example, if the operator is LESSTHANOREQUAL, and this value is a single value, the returned value will be the range from the minimum value to the single value. This allows ConstraintPhrases to be converted to a form that can be directly combined with other ConstraintPhrases from other Plays.
